# Tkinter Clock

This is a simple clock application implemented in Python using the Tkinter library. It displays the current time in a graphical window.

## Features

- Real-time clock display in HH:MM:SS format.
- Automatic time update every second.
- Minimal and user-friendly graphical interface.

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- Tkinter (usually included with Python)

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/tkinter-clock.git
cd tkinter-clock

python clock.py


